Description:
Ballistics of APFSDS-T projectile fired from the Type 73 and Type 86 smoothbore anti-tank gun. Type 73 mounts the smoothbore barrel of the Type 69 tank gun, with other parts patterned after the Soviet field gun BS-3.

Projectiles with the ballistics includes the WB125P steel penetrator, and the WB132P Tungsten-cored penetrator.

Charge:          5.655 kg  4.6 kg 9/7 + 1.055 kg 18/1 + 0.08 kg 8/1 Potassium-Rosin.
Chambrage:        1.42 (estimated)
Max Pressure:     3300 kgf/cm² [copper crusher gauge]
                 369.6 MPa     [piezoelectric]
Muzzle Velocity:  1505 m/s

Web ratio adjusted for simultaneous burnout, better reflect the design intent of mixed charge.

Performance and charge design per 《炮弹火箭弹手册：第二分册 陆军炮弹与火箭弹》. Note in 《国产火炮手册(说明部分)》 an alternative muzzle velocity of 1500 m/s is given.
